Usage in this project
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Bootstrap Icons SVG sprite file is located at:
  - public/icons/bootstrap-icons.svg

This file is used for demonstration purposes in the Icon component documentation:
  - docs/components-docs/views/icon.html
  - docs/components-docs/views/icon.ts

The SVG sprite is not bundled with the published npm package and is only used
for local development and documentation.
